header.gameNote: CHERIBUNDI TART CHERRY BOCA RATON BOWL

videos.description: Flordia Atlantic's Jason Driskel finds Willie Wright wide open in the end zone late in the first quarter to take a lead over Akron.
videos.headline: Owls on board first with easy TD

videos.description: Owls' Andew Soroh hits Zips' Van Edwards Jr extremely hard and gets a personal foul, and avoids a targeting call.
videos.headline: Florida Atlantic's Soroh drills Akron player

videos.description: Akron head coach Terry Bowden has to explain to Lane Kiffin that there are no live kangaroos in Akron.
videos.headline: Bowden throws shade at Kiffin

videos.description: Quarterback Jason Driskel takes the ball into the end zone himself for a Florida Atlantic touchdown.
videos.headline: Owls' QB walks into end zone untouched

videos.description: Devin Singletary runs for six yards for an Owl's touchdown, and his 30th rushing touchdown of the season, which breaks the conference USA record.
videos.headline: Florida Atlantic's Singletary breaks conference USA record

videos.description: Lane Kiffin is displeased with how FAU is performing vs. Akron and shares what he will tell them during the half.
videos.headline: Kiffin: 'we are not playing very good'

videos.description: Devin Singletary runs up the middle for two yards and his second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: FAU's Singletary spins up the middle for TD

videos.description: Jason Driskel connects with Willie Wright who avoids a tackle and runs in a FAU touchdown, and later runs in the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: Owls' Wright runs in TD and two-point conversion

videos.description: FAU's Jason Driskel fakes a handoff and runs the ball into the end zone to put the Owls up 43-3.
videos.headline: Owls' QB Driskel runs in TD

videos.description: Devin Singletary runs for 26 yards extending FAU's lead 50-3.
videos.headline: Owls' Singletary scores 3rd TD of game

videos.description: In the fourth quarter of FAU's rout of Akron, Lane Kiffin catches a bad pass by the Zips' quarterback on the sidelines.
videos.headline: Kiffin makes one-handed grab

videos.description: Devin Singletary runs in three touchdowns, reaching 32 on the season, and Jason Driskel combines for four scores and 337 yards as Florida Atlantic rolls to a 50-3 win.
videos.headline: Singletary, Driskel shine as FAU wins Boca Raton Bowl
